config BR2_PACKAGE_RAUC_HAWKBIT_UPDATER
	bool "rauc-hawkbit-updater"
	depends on BR2_PACKAGE_RAUC
	select BR2_PACKAGE_RAUC_JSON
	select BR2_PACKAGE_RAUC_NETWORK
	help
	  The RAUC hawkBit updater is a simple commandline tool / daemon written in C (glib). 
	  It is a port of the RAUC hawkBit Client written in Python. 
	  The daemon runs on your target and operates as an interface between the RAUC D-Bus API and the hawkBit DDI API.

	  https://github.com/rauc/rauc-hawkbit-updater
